---
/**
 * ThemeToggle — the masthead dark/light switch.
 *
 * Verbatim port of the `button.themebtn` in docs/index.html. The inline
 * `onclick="toggleTheme()"` contract is intentional: toggleTheme() is defined
 * by BaseLayout's is:inline theme bootstrap (so the button works before any
 * bundled/deferred JS runs). Do NOT convert this to an addEventListener island.
 *
 * No props: the masthead renders exactly one of these, identically on every page.
 */
---

<button
    class="themebtn"
    onclick="toggleTheme()"
    aria-label="Toggle dark mode"
    title="Toggle dark / light">🌓</button
>
